{"id": "ChIJs5SDPjon3YARyYy8loewO7E", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 499, "displayName": {"text": "Sushi Koto", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Sushi & diverse Japanese offerings in a minimalist space with glass walls & dark furnishings.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJs5SDPjon3YARyYy8loewO7E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsdWFFTkZUazFtWHpkVlJVNXBZM2t3VlRZdFMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had a great lunch at Sushi Koto and was pleasantly surprised by the quality and value.\n\nI ordered the chirashi bowl for $22.95, and it was definitely worth it. The fish was very fresh, with a nice variety and clean flavors. Everything tasted high quality, and the portion was just right—not too heavy but still filling.\n\nI also appreciated that they offer a good selection of other sushi bowls at reasonable prices, so there are plenty of options depending on what you’re in the mood for.\n\nOverall, a solid spot for fresh, well-priced sushi. Simple, satisfying, and something I would definitely come back for!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had a great lunch at Sushi Koto and was pleasantly surprised by the quality and value.\n\nI ordered the chirashi bowl for $22.95, and it was definitely worth it. The fish was very fresh, with a nice variety and clean flavors. Everything tasted high quality, and the portion was just right—not too heavy but still filling.\n\nI also appreciated that they offer a good selection of other sushi bowls at reasonable prices, so there are plenty of options depending on what you’re in the mood for.\n\nOverall, a solid spot for fresh, well-priced sushi. Simple, satisfying, and something I would definitely come back for!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ada W", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111728507229811391951/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl7Am9552xLKXwCGLpUn4OJ9LMdAZMDTZMV2xgN-st52AGnsE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-03T22:50:16.262574981Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsdWFFTkZUazFtWHpkVlJVNXBZM2t3VlRZdFMwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsdWFFTkZUazFtWHpkVlJVNXBZM2t3VlRZdFMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd273a3e8394b3:0xb13bb08796bc8cc9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs5SDPjon3YARyYy8loewO7E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsTWRGcFpjbmRNYzJwT1dGZGFORTF5V25SdWVXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The chirashi bowl here is priced reasonably and of high quality. I also enjoy their random brunch buffet. While the variety is limited, each dish is delicious and fresh.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The chirashi bowl here is priced reasonably and of high quality. I also enjoy their random brunch buffet. While the variety is limited, each dish is delicious and fresh.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Stella", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102140747968172530492/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0P5Ncto0oQNz3pJh6GR1My8-qa3GiuJQEYFTEg4xMPmdYNQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-03T16:45:48.909263955Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsTWRGcFpjbmRNYzJwT1dGZGFORTF5V25SdWVXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsTWRGcFpjbmRNYzJwT1dGZGFORTF5V25SdWVXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80dd273a3e8394b3:0xb13bb08796bc8cc9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs5SDPjon3YARyYy8loewO7E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210dU5qSkhUbnBZYTNwWlVreERiVjlWWVVOcU1GRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My friends who are OC locals told me about this spot and I am so happy they did. This restaurant serves fresh, delicious sashimi. Tried it once before and now I always think about coming back. The quality of sushi Koto is really unmatched.\n\nService is always pleasant. Always so welcoming. The sashimi here is the star of the show", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My friends who are OC locals told me about this spot and I am so happy they did. This restaurant serves fresh, delicious sashimi. Tried it once before and now I always think about coming back. The quality of sushi Koto is really unmatched.\n\nService is always pleasant. Always so welcoming. The sashimi here is the star of the show", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kathy Nguyen", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106381741056313691098/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhYDY6_gRSVUAVTSXOTKZdfKvaAyFg7KFYBJiEVMZREv2PmuuJ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-12T08:51:08.008717678Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210dU5qSkhUbnBZYTNwWlVreERiVjlWWVVOcU1GRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210dU5qSkhUbnBZYTNwWlVreERiVjlWWVVOcU1GRRAB!2m1!1s0x80dd273a3e8394b3:0xb13bb08796bc8cc9"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs5SDPjon3YARyYy8loewO7E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25SdFRUTTFiR1p1VGtwWGJUaEJNVWhNWm5CemMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "You know it's a good sushi restaurant a nt when you're the only person in the restaurant who isn't Japanese. Super good, but a bit on the pricey side for a hile in the wall.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "You know it's a good sushi restaurant a nt when you're the only person in the restaurant who isn't Japanese. Super good, but a bit on the pricey side f